<p class="lead">Start thinking. Ask questions to get your group thinking.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Is there a part of Jesus‚Äô ministry or life that you have a hard time believing or comprehending?</li>
  <li>What are some ‚ÄúChrist Plus‚Äù or ‚ÄúD-O‚Äù things you‚Äôve felt you needed to add to faith in Jesus?</li>
